{"service_name": "IBM Business Process Management (BPM)", "service_id": "7534452425346342", "company_name": "IBM United Kingdom Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     IBM United Kingdom Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     IBM Business Process Management (BPM)\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    IBM Business Process Management (BPM) leverages software and services to provide total visibility into an organisation. Discover, document, automate, and continuously improve business processes to increase efficiency and reduce costs. IBM has a services capability underpinned via a successful agile, iterative delivery methodology for successfully implementing an IBM BPM programme.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     IBM approach to BPM leverages software/services to provide:\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Collaborative process discovery using Blueworks Live, engaging business-process improvement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Social/collaboration capabilities to improve process-outcomes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Complete visibility into process activities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     IBM\u2019s Playback methodology\u2013rapid, iterative process deployment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Single shared model architecture to easily manage change\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Process optimisation\u2013robust analytics to quickly and easily improve processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     IBM BPM Methodology, with industry-leading expertise to prove business value\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Optimise business operations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Streamline tasks, real-time visibility enabling continuous process monitoring analytics\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Real-time collaboration of task management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensures work accuracy, consistency and timely completion of tasks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Manage change confidently with intuitive governance, driving process improvement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Shared reuse of process assets from a common repository\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Deliver customer engagements by extending business processes to mobile\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Drive continuous insights into business operations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     integration of business processes with core enterprise systems\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3375 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7534452425346342-pricing-document-2015-10-01-1554.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7534452425346342-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-01-1554.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7534452425346342-service-definition-document-2015-10-01-1554.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7534452425346342-terms-and-conditions-2015-10-05-1130.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vii\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 7\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      7534\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      4524\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      2534\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      6342\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       IBM United Kingdom Ltd\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        Christine Wilson\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span